class styles.models.Style(*args, **kwargs)[source]

Bases: Model

This class stores the model details of each style

Parameters:

  • name (CharField) – The name of the dance

  • category (CharField) – Two choices for the style category

  • rating (CharField) – Five choices for the dance’s rating 1 star to 5 stars

  • description (TextField) – Text description of the dance; contains the html describing the main body of the webpage

  • image (ImageField) – Image field storing an image of the dance

Returns:

The rendered index page
